{"tid":531031,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[窮L出城] 倚南窗新加坡毒遊直播（20180120-20180124）","createTime":"2018-01-16T11:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T05:45:58.000Z","uid":157601,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f5274d8f486c43a68f0c0e33a0c6b312e3ff4e67","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"<ins>前言</ins><br />\n是咁的，小弟每年都會去一次獨（毒）遊，以往毒遊地點如下：<br />\n2014 &ndash; 新加坡<br />\n2015 &ndash; 台北<br />\n2016 &ndash; 吉隆坡<br />\n2017 &ndash; 台北<br />\n2018 &ndash; 新加坡<br />\n<br />\n毒遊的好處是景點美食活動的安排一切盡在自己掌握之中，4年前的新加坡之旅充滿遺憾，原因是4日3夜的行程有接近2日的時間病倒在床，原本計劃的景點大多錯過了，早陣子剛好碰上Jetstar 減價，機票連15kg 行李只需 $10xx，於是便決定舊地重遊，買了20/1-24/1的機票，期盼能彌補一點的遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n於連登見很多人對新加坡劣評如潮，總括而言包括「消費貴、景點少、劣食多、態度差」。但我相信每一個地方的歷史、故事、特色總有其吸引之處，希望今次旅程亦能有所體會，況且小弟天性較膽小怕事，治安良好的新加坡便成為我毒遊的其中一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n通常計劃行程都會以「衣食住行」四項原則去計劃，暫時構思如下：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>衣</ins><br />\n- 無（因為窮遊）<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<ins>食</ins><br />\n- 炒粿條<br />\n- 海南雞飯<br />\n- 咖央多<br />\n- 田雞粥<br />\n- 肉骨茶<br />\n- 叻沙<br />\n- 沙嗲串燒<br />\n- 榴槤<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<ins>住</ins><br />\n- Champion Hotel City（行政單人房4晚，每晚$5xx）<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<ins>行</ins><br />\n- Chinatown (牛車水)<br />\n- Pulau Ubin (烏敏島)<br />\n- Merlion Park (魚尾獅公園)<br />\n- The Pinnacle @ Duxton (達士嶺)<br />\n- Singapore Botanic Garden (新加坡植物園)<br />\n- Little India (小印度)<br />\n- Gardens by the Bay (濱海灣花園)<br />\n<br />\n今次的直播，目標每日一早一晚出Post，早上預告當天計劃的行程，晚上則分享當日所見所聞。<br />\n第一次出post，巴絲們對於行程上有什麼建議，請不吝指教。"},{"pid":"13ba00968da00e0842e39deb85d838b0193f09ed","tid":531031,"uid":71063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"Lm 支持"},{"pid":"d7076440ae0d605762b72743d9e95b3ddaaf80d3","tid":531031,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"有無食坡妹?"},{"pid":"bbafca1dd6143f659f8a3e3e47b6baf87e1f469e","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7076440ae0d605762b72743d9e95b3ddaaf80d3","tid":531031,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"有無食坡妹?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"唔俾食坡仔咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b4aa7b314c3d803376b60d9cc3e0073196385a","tid":531031,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbafca1dd6143f659f8a3e3e47b6baf87e1f469e","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7076440ae0d605762b72743d9e95b3ddaaf80d3","tid":531031,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"有無食坡妹?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"唔俾食坡仔咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"教我ok?"},{"pid":"bbb88e71e713627de2cc79f5af966fa9994b5f55","tid":531031,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342f58e1dcdd0406c15b35227ad5f964f314507e","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bbb88e71e713627de2cc79f5af966fa9994b5f55","tid":531031,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"平靚正，我都好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eb136474023d1defe79a92bd54cb4f6461ff98","tid":531031,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/121815_24b7d3d286cedba2b14eb3d0a7a60b4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F121815_24b7d3d286cedba2b14eb3d0a7a60b4a.png&h=a2e2baf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一月二十 嘅你有冇影響呢？"},{"pid":"f22898032fbc4fd7db59e93bbe3fbc7585ec26f7","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"準備出發<br />\n<br />\n終於到了出發去新加坡今天，中午機所以無需大清早就起床。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/140544_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F140544_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4228445c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於坐廉航而小弟亦無意加錢吃頹廢飛機餐，這時候Cathay AE Card便可發揮最大功效，可免費進入環亞lounge。但當人人都有AE card的時候，我建議大家去arrival lounge，因為真的少很多人！但要預留充足時間辦出境手續。<br />\n<br />\n位置：<a href=\"https://www.plaza-network.com/location_detail?airport=Hong%20Kong%20International%20Airport&amp;city=Hong%20Kong&amp;location=Plaza%20Premium%20Lounge%20%28Arrival%20Hall%29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plaza-network.com%2Flocation_detail%3Fairport%3DHong%2520Kong%2520International%2520Airport%26city%3DHong%2520Kong%26location%3DPlaza%2520Premium%2520Lounge%2520%2528Arrival%2520Hall%2529&d=1XqBj0AsuG9BAg1bToNApS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e7a46598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.plaza-network.com/location_detail?airport=Hong%20Kong%20International%20Airport&amp;city=Hong%20Kong&amp;location=Plaza%20Premium%20Lounge%20%28Arrival%20Hall%29</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/140533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F140533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=66932ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為省卻到達新加玻才兌錢及買上網卡等問題，早幾天已在中銀預約並領取了坡紙，當然近期的rate真的很爛😫兌的時候是5.88，今天再看已經5.91，唯有慶幸自己是早了兌吧！<br />\n<br />\n而上網卡是在鴨記買的，7天無限上網$50，這個價錢真的對網速沒有期望，到埗後再試試速度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/140522_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F140522_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2fbd3bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不知何時開始此圖已成大家去旅行前指定動作，毒遊者希望今次旅程一切順利，到埗再說吧！<br />\n<br />\n最後以此歌作結。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/140456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F140456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af5c114a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/140512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F140512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1786b0cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"daf3ed9dd83bdb7f9ef14190f130e162da9f282c","tid":531031,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"4d91e0b56caf0137d2c0384b3d1d2fb053d1575a","tid":531031,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7616fbf1eb7a52b67dda42c392c96658f013a9b2","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"老巴剎有間黑胡椒炒蟹正到要再買機票去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481b4e5c0970cc1625887fdaf530c3d92cfd68e7","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n<br />\nJetstar 一如所料準時起飛，1830左右已到達新加坡樟宜機場。<br />\n<br />\n1月是新加坡的雨季，看天氣預報已大概估算到未來幾天都是下雨天。唯一的希望是：「雨，不會永遠一直下」，預報說通常是驟雨，所以未來幾天的行程都盡量比較多留在室内。<br />\n<br />\n由於想把握今日的一分一秒，我極速辦完入境手續就狗衝去T3坐地鐡(MRT)出省城，相都沒影一張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/003101_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F003101_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4d03ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等待坐Skytrain去T3前留倩影...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出到市區已經接近8點，首先去酒店check-in，Champion Hotel City 是典型新加坡式牙籤樓，入房的第一個感覺有點像劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幸好的是麻雀雖小，五臟俱全。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/003458_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F003458_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=400d7059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/003508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F003508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4f521b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肚餓非常，得知附近有知名的老巴刹美食廣場，第一時間當然狗衝過去！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/003713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F003713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ae7d5981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一進去感覺就是food court，可能時間不早，人流又不多，心想今次中伏了...原來最著名的Best Satay要穿過室内出去露天那裡，人頭湧湧，跟室内成很大對比。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/005722_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F005722_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82a1d31f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/004021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F004021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45ca9a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當我看到最小的一人份沙爹都要14sgd，雞牛各10串如此驚人的份量立即打退堂鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨便找了間店吃炒粿條(4.5sgd)味道非常普通，跟上次吃的歐南園差太遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/004918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F004918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=aa815641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/004301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F004301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=15fc8eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吃完有點意猶未盡的感覺，又經過best satay，此時有店員走來sell我，我便決定買外賣回酒店吃當宵夜，心想「幾大就幾大，燒賣就燒賣」，20串也不是太多吧！(14sgd)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/004841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F004841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60b13182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/004846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F004846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9544c826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果然味道比名不經傳的炒粿條好太多了，沙爹醬真的很正，正到難以用文字形容，加上一口一串再配青瓜等配菜也不是太誇張。如果人多可叫大份，有串燒蝦羊等等！<br />\n<br />\n吃飽漫無目的出去附近散步，酒店鄰近Clarke Quay，晚上乃著名的酒吧區，跟香港老蘭很相似，毒遊當然沒有飲獨酒的興致吧。<br />\n<br />\n雖說天氣不好，但晚上竟出了月亮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/010218_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F010218_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3d8f3993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n忽然又想起一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/010501_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F010501_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=57d37770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/005652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F005652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=14fcb7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在河邊走著走著，「也許我是走得太累，也許，也許我要睡一睡」，真的有點累了，最後決定回去休息，明天繼續。"},{"pid":"79087e5ef11644fd2bbf740e969a63968aa1edbf","tid":531031,"uid":52162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"想試下去sg食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99306ba6fc7a0d3f000799447a82237c9e8f185b","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7616fbf1eb7a52b67dda42c392c96658f013a9b2","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"老巴剎有間黑胡椒炒蟹正到要再買機票去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"一個人食好似太多，所以無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339844823cbf96c2b3b5d6062947e36d8b3e2652","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d91e0b56caf0137d2c0384b3d1d2fb053d1575a","tid":531031,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7c2bc3e51aa36a17c6d142e0a5255d4336afd6","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99306ba6fc7a0d3f000799447a82237c9e8f185b","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7616fbf1eb7a52b67dda42c392c96658f013a9b2","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"老巴剎有間黑胡椒炒蟹正到要再買機票去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"一個人食好似太多，所以無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"我都一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁叫一隻都得架"},{"pid":"ad511c7df2b0974d9c99fe97886207cde4719663","tid":531031,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"1）路邊麵包夾雪糕消暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）唔知係india/bugis有間叫zam zam既印度野食<br />\n樓上/樓下收費唔同，樓上有冷氣<br />\n3）garden by the bay唔好朝早去<br />\n旁晚去左2個館影下相，等夜晚睇濕9show<br />\n同埋好似有得上skyway鳩下<br />\n4）唔好去個咩夜晚動物園，睇佢地訓覺<br />\n真係伏到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5）食野hawker center唔貴選擇又多<br />\n海南雞/雲吞麵（無湯唔係香港個款）<br />\n炒果條（河粉好味啲）/laksa<br />\n但係椰漿飯就伏黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSG老麥個脆辣雞腿包又熱又辣仲可以雙層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6）印象china town有間找換店平過香港<br />\n好多人排隊，唔夠洗可以去個到睇下個rate<br />\n<br />\n留名睇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩得開心啲，小心尾班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817bbcab6562f2a3c3a12ded76f9dbf20d053659","tid":531031,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"老巴剎外面1條街有檔賣奶茶排晒長龍好好飲的"},{"pid":"ec0f5f80d230f416a5afdd2cac0d2d160ec5d2f2","tid":531031,"uid":5720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7c2bc3e51aa36a17c6d142e0a5255d4336afd6","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99306ba6fc7a0d3f000799447a82237c9e8f185b","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7616fbf1eb7a52b67dda42c392c96658f013a9b2","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"老巴剎有間黑胡椒炒蟹正到要再買機票去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"一個人食好似太多，所以無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"我都一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁叫一隻都得架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:42:23.000Z","msg":"之前我都試過一個人食黑胡椒炒蟹<br />\n不過我食果間係芽籠果邊同永成（兩間KC 都有介紹過）"},{"pid":"d8e0552862bc445e3eaa18b6aa2c4d4e64a26759","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad511c7df2b0974d9c99fe97886207cde4719663","tid":531031,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"1）路邊麵包夾雪糕消暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）唔知係india/bugis有間叫zam zam既印度野食<br />\n樓上/樓下收費唔同，樓上有冷氣<br />\n3）garden by the bay唔好朝早去<br />\n旁晚去左2個館影下相，等夜晚睇濕9show<br />\n同埋好似有得上skyway鳩下<br />\n4）唔好去個咩夜晚動物園，睇佢地訓覺<br />\n真係伏到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5）食野hawker center唔貴選擇又多<br />\n海南雞/雲吞麵（無湯唔係香港個款）<br />\n炒果條（河粉好味啲）/laksa<br />\n但係椰漿飯就伏黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSG老麥個脆辣雞腿包又熱又辣仲可以雙層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6）印象china town有間找換店平過香港<br />\n好多人排隊，唔夠洗可以去個到睇下個rate<br />\n<br />\n留名睇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩得開心啲，小心尾班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:29:21.000Z","msg":"麵包夾雪糕個伯伯係魚尾獅公園附近<br />\n威化餅夾雪糕個伯伯係牛車水<br />\n兩個都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾特別"},{"pid":"616d750478789a4782dd80c3158b2115210189da","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec0f5f80d230f416a5afdd2cac0d2d160ec5d2f2","tid":531031,"uid":5720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7c2bc3e51aa36a17c6d142e0a5255d4336afd6","tid":531031,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99306ba6fc7a0d3f000799447a82237c9e8f185b","tid":531031,"uid":157601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"一個人食好似太多，所以無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"我都一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁叫一隻都得架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:42:23.000Z","msg":"之前我都試過一個人食黑胡椒炒蟹<br />\n不過我食果間係芽籠果邊同永成（兩間KC 都有介紹過）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:34:11.000Z","msg":"我食個間叫Yong Kee 伙記好nice 識廣東話<br />\n<br />\n但隔離鋪個肥婆好撚冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n追住問我係咪香港人 我路過又唔係幫襯廢時應佢<br />\n佢話我係咪聾 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415df8307ee17e7f1f73f76ace0741a944a88c53","tid":531031,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad511c7df2b0974d9c99fe97886207cde4719663","tid":531031,"uid":15084